platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Is there anything more inspiring than learning from a master? This app is built on the principle that watching the greatest living artists, creators, and athletes share the secrets of their craft can be life-changing.

Is there anything more inspiring than learning from a master? This app is built on the principle that watching the greatest living artists, creators and athletes share the secrets of their craft can be life-changing.
如果能跟隨大師學習，想必獲益良多。這款 App 以此原則為本，讓你有機會觀看當今多位偉大的藝術家、創作者和運動員分享其獨到技巧及心得，甚至為生活帶來改變。

Is there anything more inspiring than learning from a master? The MasterClass app is built on the principle that watching the greatest living artists, creators and athletes share the secrets of their craft can be life-changing.
